constraints: Intro: Protons (parcan_pl & parcan_pr) flash 100ms each beat to mimic synth rhythm.
No fixture kept steady >2 beats: pars update every beat; moving head updated every 1-2 beats.

head_behavior.goal: follow lyrics with gentle movement; mostly on
notes: During detected vocal sections: small sweeps around preset.
During instrumental sections: slow drift moves.

head_style.description: Continuous, legato, non-beat-locked movement dancing to melody.
design_rules: Motion decoupled from strict beat grid

head_dimmer_policy.goal: Keep moving head visible while moving
